org.apache.juneau.http.header

Class BasicCsvArrayHeader

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.juneau.http.BasicHeader
      • org.apache.juneau.http.header.BasicCsvArrayHeader
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable, Cloneable, Header, NameValuePair
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    Allow, ContentLanguage, Upgrade, Via

    public class BasicCsvArrayHeader
extends BasicHeader
    Category of headers that consist of a comma-delimited list of string values.

    Example

    Allow: GET, PUT

    • Hypertext Transfer Protocol -- HTTP/1.1
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
